data.description: Come check out this adorable ranch home in Coventry LSD. This home is conveniently located close to all the Portage Lakes has to offer. Within minutes of the Lakes, Restaurants, Shopping, Laundry, Parks and much more. This lovely home features vinyl siding, vinyl windows, newer furnace, new paint throughout, new LVP flooring, new light fixtures and a brand new stove. Good sized lot with a freshly painted deck. Schedule a showing today to make this house your home. Agent Interest.
